==============================================================================
LEGAL COMPLIANCE: WiZ BULB CONTROLLER PROTOCOL
==============================================================================

The WiZ light integration module inside this application (backend/wiz.py) is 
fully legal, compliant, and does not violate any proprietary intellectual 
property or terms of service:
- It relies entirely on standard built-in Python socket libraries (`socket`).
- It communicates via standard, open JSON-RPC UDP commands broadcast to port 
  38899 on the local area network, which is the native local protocol exposed 
  by WiZ hardware.
- It does not contain, distribute, or unpack any reverse-engineered, encrypted, 
  or proprietary proprietary blobs or firmware.

