* Uvicorn (BSD 3-Clause License) - ASGI server.
* mss (MIT License) - Screen capture utility.
* Pillow (HPND License) - Image processing library.
* mcp (MIT License) - Model Context Protocol SDK.
* requests (Apache 2.0 License) - HTTP library.
* httpx (BSD 3-Clause License) - HTTP client.
* openrgb-python (MIT License) - OpenRGB SDK client.
* winsdk (MIT License) - WinRT Windows APIs.

